data.description:
Charming ranch-style home in Stow-Munroe Falls CSD with two bedrooms and one bath. Situated on a spacious .35-acre lot, this well-maintained property features a newer roof and hot water tank for worry-free living. The kitchen comes equipped with a gas stove and
refrigerator, and the laundry/utility room includes a washer and dryer.
Enjoy the convenience of an eat-in kitchen, a comfortable living room, and a family room perfect for gatherings. Patio doors lead to the
outside, where you'll find a lovely yard and a two-car detached garage. The primary bedroom boasts hardwood floors and a walk-in
closet.
Additional features include central air for year-round comfort, public water and sewer services, and a home warranty for added peace
of mind. This home is ideally located near main roads and highways, providing easy access to amenities and commuter routes. Don't
miss the opportunity to make this delightful property your new home.
